    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total dream. It\u2019s been kept in such pristine condition that it honestly feels like it just left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged and kept sparkling clean inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m really looking for a great new home for it, so if you want a ride that\u2019s practically flawless, drop me a message! I'm super happy to chat and answer any questions you have!",
