    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L inline-six delivers razor-sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, with the VANOS system meticulously serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and corner-exit rotation. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Every bushing, from the control arms to the trailing links, remains compliant yet firm, preserving the legendary communicative steering rack. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster\u2014a true collector-grade specimen that performs exactly as Munich intended.",
      "price": 46500.0,
